  <div class="box en">🎯 <strong>What to watch:</strong> ① When the Commission's final proposal is published and whether it includes an equivalence clause ② Whether the scope expands to tokenized payments and deposits ③ How individual issuers like Circle and Tether respond ④ Whether national regulators' existing authorization backlog affects their capacity to take on new obligations</div>
